The result of the vote of the 15 member countries of <COREF ID="7" TYPE="IDENT">the Security Council</COREF> was : 9 votes for <COREF ID="3" TYPE="IDENT">the proposal</COREF> , 2 votes against and 4 votes abstaining .
<COREF ID="4" TYPE="IDENT">The US</COREF> , <COREF ID="1" TYPE="IDENT">the UK</COREF> , France and Russia voted for <COREF ID="3" TYPE="IDENT">the proposal</COREF> and China abstained .
